https://www.gnu.org/software/datamash/manual/html_node/Reverse-and-Transpose.html
$ cat input.txt
Sample   Year   Count
A        2014   1002
B        2013    990
C        2014   2030
D        2014    599

$ datamash transpose < input.txt
Sample  A       B       C       D
Year    2014    2013    2014    2014
Count   1002    990     2030    599